Summary: Biochemical reaction from atomoxetine to 4'-hydroxy atomoxetine. This interaction is catalyzed by CYP2D6.
Biochemical reaction from atomoxetine to N-desmethyl atomoxetine. This interaction is catalyzed by CYP2C19.
Biochemical reaction from atomoxetine to 2-hydroxymethyl atomoxetine. This interaction can be catalyzed by CYP2B6 or CYP2D6.
Biochemical reaction from N-desmethyl-4-hydroxyatomoxetine to N-desmethyl-4-hydroxyatomoxetine glucuronide.
Biochemical reaction from atomoxetine to 4'-hydroxy atomoxetine. This interaction can be catalyzed by CYP2C19, CYP2E1, CYP3A4, CYP1A2 or CYP2B6.
Biochemical reaction from N-desmethyl atomoxetine to N-desmethyl-4-hydroxyatomoxetine. This interaction is catalyzed by CYP2D6.
